 Governmental, National Laboratory WWW Sites for Microscopy & Microanalysis

   This is a collection of Governmental Organizations that maintain WWW
   sites and have a connection with Microscopy and Microanalysis. The list
   is by no means comprehensive and should you have suggestions for
   additions I will be pleased to add them. See directions at the bottom
   of this page.
     __________________________________________________________________

  Sites in the United States of America
     __________________________________________________________________

     * Microscopy & Microanalysis Site at ANL
     * TelePresence Microscopy Site at ANL
     * DoE 2000 Materials MicroCharacterization Collaboratory
     * Other U.S. Dept. of Energy Research Sites
     * National Center for Electron Microscopy at Lawrence Berkeley
       Laboratory
     * 3D REconstruction, NASA Ames Biocomputation Center
     * Lawrence Berkeley Imaging and Distributed Computing Group
     * Secondary Ion Mass Spectrometry Server at National Institute of
       Standards and Technology (NIST)
     * USGS Denver Electron Microprobe Lab
     * NCI Veterinary and Tumor Pathology Section of the Office of
       Laboratory Animal Science (OLAS)
     * Distributed, Collaboratory Experiment Environments (DCEE) Program
     * National Museum of Natural History SEM LabSmithsonian Institution,
       Washington, DC
     * Scanning Transmission Electron Microscope-NIH Research Resource at
       Brookhaven National Laboratory
     __________________________________________________________________

  Sites in Europe
     __________________________________________________________________

     * ESCA Microscope , Elettra synchrotron source, Trieste
     * Raman Microscopy Lab at Materials Science Institute (CSIC), Madrid,
       Spain
     * Electron Microscopy Department Centro de Investigacion y Control de
       la Calidad, Madrid, Spain
     * Center of Applied Physics Dubna, Moscow region, Russia
       Interests: Physical Sciences
     __________________________________________________________________

  Sites in Australia, Asia & The South Pacific
     __________________________________________________________________

     * Australian Nuclear Science and Technology Organization , Menai
       (Sydney), NSW, Australia
     * NRIM Atom Probe Laboratory, National Research Institute for Metals,
       Tsukuba, Japan
     __________________________________________________________________

